    {"topic":"Mind-Body Problem","difficulty":"hard","question":"Higher-order theories of consciousness (Rosenthal) hold that a mental state is conscious iff:","options":["It is a brain state","It is accompanied by a suitable higher-order mental state that represents it","It is accessible to introspection","It plays a functional role"],"answer":1},
