    {"topic":"Sartre","difficulty":"medium","question":"For Sartre, the 'Other' (l'Autre) threatens the subject by:","options":["Offering new freedoms","The gaze — objectifying consciousness and potentially reducing the subject to an object","Sharing one's freedom","Creating intersubjective solidarity"],"answer":1},
