    {"topic":"Foucault","difficulty":"medium","question":"Foucault's 'bio-power' (biopower) refers to:","options":["The power of biological organisms","Power that governs and regulates human populations as biological entities","Individual physical strength","Military power over bodies"],"answer":1},
